thread.title: Shaquille O'Neal absolutely dwarfs gymnastics star Simone Biles in this Super Bowl photo
thread.title_full: Shaquille O'Neal absolutely dwarfs gymnastics star Simone Biles in this Super Bowl photo

title: Shaquille O'Neal absolutely dwarfs gymnastics star Simone Biles in this Super Bowl photo
text:
Feb 5, 2017 at 5:20p ET 0Shares 
Shaquille O’Neal made fellow NBA players look tiny during his Hall of Fame career. But to really understand how large O’Neal is, take a peek at this photo he took with 4-foot-9 U.S. gymnastics star Simone Biles before Super Bowl LI. 
— Simone Biles (@Simone_Biles) February 5, 2017 
Take note that Biles, who won four gold medals at the Rio Olympics, is wearing heels in this photo, too. But to be fair, most everyone would look small standing next to one of the most dominating players in NBA history. 0
